{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_08_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 2話 みんなと一緒に進むこと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――怜が仕事に復帰してから、数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days after Rei returned to work",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nもう一度、私と遙子さんでユニットを組ませて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚\nPlease let Haruko-san and I form a unit again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5000000079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "急にどうしたんだ？\nユニットバトルはもう終わったんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's gotten into you all of a sudden?\nThe unit battle is already over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5333332141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.1209749143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "それは分かってます。でも、せっかくの遙子さんの\n想いを、こんな形のまま終わらせたくないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know that. But I don't want to leave Haruko-san's feelings\nhanging like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.5758703365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.3370744627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になってから、私はずっと悩んでました\nここからさらに上を目指すにはどうしたらいいのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since we became BIG4‚ I've been worried.\nHow can we aim even higher from here…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3666665475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "悩んで、考えて、それでも答えが出なくて\n一人で焦って空回りして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I worried‚ I thought‚ but I couldn't find the answer‚\nso I was just getting impatient and spinning my wheels.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9333332141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.7241747142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "そんな私に、遙子さんは新しいユニットを組むことで\n自分を見つめ直す機会を作ってくれたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san gave me a chance to re-evaluate myself\nby forming a new unit with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7333360116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、サニピから離れて活動することが\n怜の視野を広げることに繋がると思ったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ she thought that working away from Sunny Peace\nwould help broaden your horizons‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2333360116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.5848098994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに、mihoさんから指摘されるまで\n私は遙子さんの真意に気付きませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But despite that‚ I didn't realize Haruko-san's true intentions\nbefore miho-san pointed it out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0666693449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "しかもユニットバトルではあんな負け方をして……\nこのまま終わったら、私は悔やんでも悔やみきれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And we lost the unit battle in such a way…\nIf we end it like this‚ I'll regret it forever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.8666693449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.8666693449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、ユニットバトルは\n途中棄権という不本意な終わり方だったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true that the unit battle…\n…ended in an unexpected way with us withdrawing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7000026782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.0124290388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんは尊敬出来る素敵なアイドルです\nその遙子さんが私のためにユニットを組んでくれた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san is a wonderful idol I respect.\nShe formed a unit with me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2000026782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんが私を支えてくれていたように\n私も遙子さんの魅力を引き出したいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just like how Haruko-san supported me…\n…I want to bring out Haruko-san's charm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.3000026782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.935331464
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "二人で最高のステージを作り上げたいんです\nお願いします、もう一度だけチャンスを下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to create the best stage together with her.\nPlease‚ give us one more chance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4666693449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.0812044067
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "チャンスか……実は今度、二人組のアイドル限定の\nライブイベントが開催されることになったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A chance‚ huh… Actually‚ there's a live event coming up\nthat's exclusively for duo idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7000026782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロにも参加のオファーが来ていたんだが……\n怜、遙子さんと出てみるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoshimi Production also received an offer to participate…\nRei‚ do you want to participate with Haruko-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3666693449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.0865561408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\n私と遙子さんのユニットで参加させて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!\nPlease let our unit‚ Haruko-san and I‚ participate!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.6000026782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "今度こそ悔いのないように\n納得のいくパフォーマンスをしてみせます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time‚ I'll make sure\nto deliver a performance I'm satisfied with!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7666713794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.4561271908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんと、悔いのないように……\n今度こそ、絶対に……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san and I‚ without any regrets…\nThis time‚ for sure…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.8000047128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.694245283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 142.760925174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "イベントに向けて、怜と遙子さんのユニットも\n順調に仕上がってきているな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei and Haruko-san's unit\nare coming along well for the event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ユニットバトルの時はずっとピリピリしていた怜も\nすっかり落ち着いて、練習も和やかな雰囲気だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei‚ who was always tense during the unit battle\nhas calmed down completely‚ and practice has a peaceful atmosphere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.0333512705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nお先に失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚\nI'll be leaving now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.2333512705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、もう上がるのか？\n怜はまだまだ余力がありそうに見えたが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? You're leaving already?\nRei‚ you looked like you still had some energy left",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.3666846038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "この間は練習をし過ぎたせいで疲れが溜まって\nミスに繋がりましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I practiced too much last time‚ and the fatigue\nled to mistakes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.6000179371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "今回は遙子さんの意見を取り入れて\n無理のない軽めの練習でいくことにしたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time‚ we're taking Haruko-san's advice\nand doing light practice without overdoing it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.2000179371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今までの怜とは真逆の方針だが、それで平気なのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's the opposite approach from your usual‚ Rei‚ are you okay with that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.9600109818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんにも同じことを聞かれましたが、私に任せると\n焦ったり無理したり突っ走ったりしてしまいますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san asked me the same thing‚ but if I'm left in charge‚\nI'll get impatient‚ push myself too hard‚ and rush things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.5333512705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "視野の広い遙子さんの意見に合わせた方が\nいい結果に繋がるはずです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's better to follow Haruko-san's lead\nsince she has a broader perspective. I believe it will lead to better results.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.4666846038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんのためにも、無理せず落ち着いて\n今度こそ、いい結果を出してみせます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For Haruko-san's sake‚ I'll stay calm‚ avoid overdoing it\nand deliver good results this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.5666846038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（確かに調子は良さそうだが、一方的に合わせるのも）\n（それはそれでいいことなのか……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She certainly seems to be in good shape‚ but is it a good thing\nto just go along with everything?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.6666662933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブイベントが間近に迫った、ある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day‚ with the live event fast approaching",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.6748895091,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-evening",
      "startTime": 219.1415429515
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "どうしよう……今更こんなこと……\nやっぱりこのままの方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I do…? To bring this up now…\nMaybe it's better to just leave it as it is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.7333258392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "様子を見に来てみれば、案の定だな……\n怜、何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I came to check on you‚ and as I thought…\nRei‚ is something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.0999925059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん\nいえ、大したことじゃありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san…\nIt's nothing‚ really.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.1333258392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうは見えないぞ\n悩みがあるなら、なんでも相談してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't look like it's nothing.\nIf you're troubled‚ talk to me about anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.4333258392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "悩みって……うぅ、そんなに私、分かりやすいかな\nでも、本当に大したことじゃないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Troubled…? Ugh‚ am I that easy to read?\nBut it's really nothing serious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.8333258392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんと練習していて、もっと振り付けのレベルを\n上げてもいいんじゃないかと思ってしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was practicing with Haruko-san‚ and I was thinking\nmaybe we should increase the level of the choreography…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.3666591725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けは大変になりますが\nその方がもっといいパフォーマンスになるかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It will make the choreography more difficult‚\nbut I think it would make for a better performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.4999925059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "だが、イベントまであまり日数がないぞ\n今から振り付けを難しくしたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there's not much time left until the event.\nIf you make the choreography more difficult now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 276.8666591725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "はい、どうしても練習時間を増やすことになります\nここで無理をしたら、失敗した前回の二の舞です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ we'll definitely have to increase practice time.\nIf we push ourselves too hard here‚ we'll just repeat the same mistakes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.1333258392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei026.m4a",
      "text": "だから、答えは出てるんです\nこのままの振り付けでいった方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I know the answer.\nIt's better to go with the current choreography…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 294.1666591725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "でも、本心ではそう思っていないんだろ？\nだからそんなに悩んでいるんじゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you don't really feel that way‚ do you?\nThat's why you're so conflicted‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.2333482189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei027.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私がどう思うかは関係ありません\n遙子さんにも、ユニットバトルの時に話したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-It doesn't matter what I think.\nI told Haruko-san during the unit battle",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 306.6333299084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei028.m4a",
      "text": "焦らないでみんなと一緒に進んで行くって。もう無理に\n私のやり方に遙子さんを巻き込みたくありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "that I wouldn't rush and would move forward together with everyone.\nI don't want to force Haruko-san into my way of doing things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 317.3666571382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "怜、それは本当に\n『みんなと一緒に進む』ことなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei‚ is that truly\n\"moving forward together\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 324.3333238049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei029.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 327.2010637048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、前回はやり方が悪かったかもしれない\nだが、それで怜の全てが否定される訳じゃないだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true that your approach might have been wrong last time‚\nbut that doesn't mean everything you do is wrong‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 331.9666713797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "怜には怜の考え方があるし、遙子さんには遙子さんの\n考え方がある。それを踏まえて、二人で決めていく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have your own way of thinking‚ Rei‚ and Haruko-san has hers.\nTake those into consideration and decide together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 339.8000047131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "それが、二人で……\n『みんなと一緒に進む』ことだと俺は思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That is\n\"moving forward together\" in my opinion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 346.7333380464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei030.m4a",
      "text": "二人で、決めていく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Decide together",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 350.7801026745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei031.m4a",
      "text": "……確かに私は、我慢して自分の気持ちを抑え込んで\n遙子さんの歩幅に合わせて進もうとしてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I was trying to suppress my own feelings\nand adjust to Haruko-san's pace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 360.4666713797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei032.m4a",
      "text": "でも、歩幅は一人で決めるものじゃない\n遙子さんと一緒に決めるものだったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the pace isn't something you decide on your own.\nIt's something you decide together with Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 369.1666652762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。一人の力では難しいことも、仲間と一緒なら\n頑張れるし、さらにいい方向へ進んで行けるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Even things that are difficult to do alone‚\nyou can work hard and move forward in a better direction.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 376.9666652762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei033.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね。一人で走るより、周りと一緒に\n頑張る方が私も成長出来る気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right. I feel like I can grow more\nif I work hard with others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 386.1666978284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-rei034.m4a",
      "text": "さっそく遙子さんと相談して、最高のステージに\nなるように練習メニューを考え直します！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll talk to Haruko-san right away and we'll reconsider\nthe practice plan to make it the best stage possible!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 393.433364495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_02-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "気合いを入れ過ぎて\n突っ走らないようにな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't get too fired up\nand rush into things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 398.6333889091,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
